@startuml

title Codegen entity meta-model — Keys and columns (structural)

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0

class Entity <<metaclass>> {
  +keysAndColumns : KeysAndColumns
}

class KeysAndColumns <<segment>> {
  +schema : string
  +product : string
  +component : string
}

class PrimaryKey <<segment>> {
  +column : string
  +type : string
  +cppType : string
}

class NaturalKey <<segment>> {
  +column : string
  +type : string
  +cppType : string
}

class Column <<segment>> {
  +type : string
  +cppType : string
  +nullable : boolean
}

note right of KeysAndColumns
  has_tenant_id and has_workspace_id
  are not drawn here -- they are
  non-structural features, not fields
  of the entity itself. See this page's
  UVL feature diagram.
end note

Entity --> KeysAndColumns
KeysAndColumns "1" *-- "1" PrimaryKey
KeysAndColumns "1" *-- "0..*" NaturalKey
KeysAndColumns "1" *-- "0..*" Column

@enduml
